WEBVTT

00:15.460 --> 00:19.960
♪During the dark night♪

00:20.100 --> 00:22.750
♪A guiding light♪

00:23.260 --> 00:25.050
♪Just like you♪

00:25.460 --> 00:29.750
♪Makes life turn bright♪

00:30.330 --> 00:35.180
♪Breaking free from darkness♪

00:35.400 --> 00:38.880
♪You gave me strength♪

00:39.230 --> 00:41.780
♪Running for truth♪

00:41.800 --> 00:45.850
♪I find my path♪

00:46.600 --> 00:50.580
♪Drawing on the hope♪

00:51.200 --> 00:54.580
♪That you render me♪

00:55.130 --> 00:58.010
♪In this long journey♪

00:58.260 --> 01:01.680
♪I run on lightly♪

01:19.180 --> 01:22.980
[Reborn]
[Adapted from Qiang Yu's work, Reborn]

01:24.260 --> 01:27.610
[2007, Nanqiao Village, Shunyun County]

01:29.780 --> 01:32.160
[Shunyun to Huanzhou]

01:37.740 --> 01:39.990
[Shunyun to Huanzhou]

01:51.250 --> 01:51.850
Do you want some?

02:08.970 --> 02:09.770
Hello?

02:09.770 --> 02:11.770
I'm the landlady.

02:12.090 --> 02:13.010
Hello, ma'am.

02:13.010 --> 02:13.530
Yes.

02:13.530 --> 02:15.730
Well, the property management fee...

02:16.610 --> 02:17.010
Wait.

02:17.010 --> 02:18.210
Didn't you only ask for a transfer fee?

02:18.210 --> 02:20.290
I've already paid 80,000 in full.

02:20.290 --> 02:22.130
Why would there be
a property management fee?

02:22.130 --> 02:23.250
Ma'am,

02:23.250 --> 02:24.730
we're doing a small business.

02:24.730 --> 02:25.530
I'm so sorry, sir.

02:25.530 --> 02:26.410
Please cut us some slack.

02:26.410 --> 02:26.650
It's all right.

02:26.650 --> 02:28.690
To be honest, we handle
the cleaning and rubbish

02:28.690 --> 02:30.770
every day ourselves.

02:30.770 --> 02:31.450
We don't need a management service.

02:31.450 --> 02:32.450
Do you still care
about your eyesight or what?

02:32.450 --> 02:34.690
Yes, of course I do.

02:34.690 --> 02:36.050
I'll pay.

02:36.050 --> 02:37.530
Good. When will you pay?

02:37.530 --> 02:39.010
By the end of the year. Is that okay?

02:39.010 --> 02:39.690
Hello?

02:39.690 --> 02:41.250
I'll pay.

02:49.930 --> 02:52.170
Sir, drive carefully.

02:52.170 --> 02:53.690
My water spilled.

03:05.650 --> 03:08.410
Everyone used to tell me,

03:08.410 --> 03:09.770
"Just grow up.

03:10.850 --> 03:13.370
Everything gets better
when you're older."

03:16.970 --> 03:17.810
But why,

03:18.850 --> 03:20.530
the older I get,

03:20.530 --> 03:22.610
[Huanzhou]
the more confused I've become?

03:30.010 --> 03:35.010
[Episode 1]
[Beiyu's Little Sister?]

03:35.410 --> 03:40.250
[Qiao's Handmade Noodle House]

03:40.250 --> 03:44.650
Grand Opening!

04:10.910 --> 04:13.010
[Tripe slices, 4 yuan]

04:13.010 --> 04:14.710
[Oyster, 5 yuan]

04:14.710 --> 04:16.110
[Intestines, 5 yuan]

04:19.769 --> 04:21.370
Hello, feel free to try
Qiao's Handmade Noodle House.

04:22.650 --> 04:23.970
Hello, this is
Qiao's Handmade Noodle House.

04:24.330 --> 04:25.610
Come try Qiao's Handmade Noodle House.

04:26.290 --> 04:28.610
Fair price and generous portions.

04:28.610 --> 04:29.170
Exactly.

04:29.690 --> 04:30.170
[Qiao's Handmade Noodle House]

04:30.170 --> 04:32.050
Hello, come try
Qiao's Handmade Noodle House.

04:32.050 --> 04:34.530
It's the shop's opening. Welcome.

04:34.530 --> 04:35.730
Qiao's Handmade Noodle House.

04:36.450 --> 04:38.650
Fair price and generous portions.

04:39.010 --> 04:39.409
You...

04:42.850 --> 04:43.730
No.

04:43.730 --> 04:45.370
Hello, feel free to try
Qiao's Handmade Noodle House.

04:50.570 --> 04:52.450
It doesn't look like a proper opening.

04:53.010 --> 04:54.010
We only set off
two strings of firecrackers.

04:54.010 --> 04:55.210
Do people even know what we're doing?

04:56.090 --> 04:57.250
When we opened in our hometown,

04:57.250 --> 04:59.010
you prepared two flower baskets.

04:59.010 --> 05:00.770
Now, nothing is ready.

05:00.770 --> 05:02.770
And everything is in a mess.

05:02.770 --> 05:03.570
I don't get it.

05:03.570 --> 05:05.490
Why do you have to choose today?

05:08.650 --> 05:10.410
Didn't I tell you?

05:10.410 --> 05:11.610
The date is picked.

05:11.890 --> 05:13.410
Today is a good day
to start the business.

05:14.250 --> 05:15.610
Yes, I guess so.

05:18.650 --> 05:20.650
This small shop

05:21.010 --> 05:22.290
actually costs 80,000
for the transfer fee.

05:22.650 --> 05:23.690
Aside from that,

05:24.010 --> 05:25.810
there's also a property management fee.
I've never heard of it.

05:26.610 --> 05:27.570
You know,

05:27.570 --> 05:29.090
I bought some green veggies
this morning.

05:29.490 --> 05:30.810
It was 0.8 yuan more per kilogram.

05:30.810 --> 05:32.730
It was less than that
back in our hometown.

05:32.970 --> 05:34.330
Why didn't you mention

05:34.330 --> 05:36.050
we could sell a few more yuan
for each bowl of noodles?

05:36.250 --> 05:36.850
Who do we sell the noodles to?

05:37.290 --> 05:37.890
No one's here.

05:40.010 --> 05:40.530
What happened?

05:41.890 --> 05:42.690
Mom.

05:44.330 --> 05:45.250
Did you get hurt?

05:47.090 --> 05:48.010
Don't move.

05:48.890 --> 05:50.409
Pieces for peace.
Everything is going well.

05:50.409 --> 05:51.530
Enough.

05:51.530 --> 05:53.090
You two go hand out fliers.

05:53.090 --> 05:54.130
I'll clean up here.

05:55.130 --> 05:55.770
All right. Go on.

05:56.490 --> 05:57.290
Be careful.

05:57.290 --> 05:57.970
I'll do it. Give it to me.

05:58.610 --> 05:59.170
Where's Jinyu?

05:59.610 --> 06:00.090
At the door.

06:07.490 --> 06:09.650
Nice shot! Yeah!

06:10.810 --> 06:11.690
You rascal.

06:11.690 --> 06:12.970
Why didn't you tell me you went out?

06:13.330 --> 06:15.250
Can't you learn from your sister
and help us out?

06:15.250 --> 06:16.050
The noodle house is all busy.

06:17.010 --> 06:17.930
I haven't paid yet.

06:20.170 --> 06:20.810
Ma'am,

06:20.810 --> 06:23.210
today's the first day
of our noodle house.

06:23.210 --> 06:24.250
We haven't made any profits yet.

06:24.730 --> 06:25.650
How about this?

06:25.930 --> 06:27.490
I'll bring you a bowl of noodles.

06:28.490 --> 06:29.370
Is that your shop?

06:29.370 --> 06:29.930
Yes.

06:29.930 --> 06:30.770
Don't worry.

06:30.770 --> 06:32.330
We're neighbors.

06:32.810 --> 06:33.890
We'll pay you back tomorrow.

06:33.890 --> 06:35.090
It's all right.

06:35.650 --> 06:36.330
Fliers.

06:36.530 --> 06:37.610
Right. Fliers.

06:37.610 --> 06:38.290
He's naughty.

06:39.250 --> 06:40.210
How many children do you have?

06:40.570 --> 06:41.170
Two.

06:42.130 --> 06:43.170
She's the elder one, right?

06:45.690 --> 06:46.970
It's good to have a boy and a girl.

06:46.970 --> 06:48.010
You'll have a comfortable life
ahead of you.

06:48.010 --> 06:48.650
Thanks, you as well.

06:48.650 --> 06:51.050
All the best for your new business.

06:51.050 --> 06:51.409
Thank you, ma'am.

06:51.409 --> 06:53.290
Drop by anytime.

06:53.290 --> 06:53.970
Sure.

06:53.970 --> 06:54.650
We will.

06:55.970 --> 06:56.409
Go in.

06:59.690 --> 07:00.410
How blessed.

07:06.050 --> 07:07.610
You splashed dirty water in my bowl!

07:09.170 --> 07:09.970
I didn't.

07:09.970 --> 07:10.890
The cloth is dry.

07:10.890 --> 07:12.290
I saw the water splash over here.

07:12.930 --> 07:14.690
Are you sure you saw that?

07:14.690 --> 07:15.850
What's with your attitude?

07:16.290 --> 07:17.410
Do you have no manners?

07:17.690 --> 07:18.090
Fanghao.

07:18.090 --> 07:18.730
I'll teach you some manners!

07:19.010 --> 07:19.890
Say that again!

07:21.890 --> 07:22.570
What happened?

07:22.570 --> 07:23.410
Let me see.

07:23.410 --> 07:24.250
No, don't go over there.

07:24.250 --> 07:25.210
You're supposed to be providing service.

07:25.210 --> 07:26.210
What's with your attitude?

07:26.690 --> 07:27.810
He called me blind.

07:27.810 --> 07:28.490
Sorry.

07:28.490 --> 07:29.250
What's wrong with this brat?

07:29.250 --> 07:29.890
Please calm down.

07:29.890 --> 07:30.570
You're his mom?

07:30.770 --> 07:31.850
He called me blind.

07:32.650 --> 07:33.610
Please sit down and calm down.

07:33.690 --> 07:34.330
Well.

07:34.370 --> 07:35.290
Put it down.

07:36.330 --> 07:38.010
Why are you so careless?

07:38.090 --> 07:38.810
He was using a cloth

07:39.090 --> 07:40.930
and splashed dirty water
into my noodles!

07:41.010 --> 07:41.730
Please sit down and calm down.

07:41.730 --> 07:43.490
I'll prepare a new bowl of noodles.
It won't take long.

07:44.570 --> 07:45.930
What a temper.

07:49.450 --> 07:50.890
Here's a new bowl of noodles for you.

07:51.770 --> 07:53.850
I'm too pissed to eat anything else.

08:07.250 --> 08:08.290
Why is the tire flat?

08:11.890 --> 08:13.010
Bummer.

08:17.850 --> 08:19.170
I didn't even touch her.

08:19.170 --> 08:20.010
That's enough.

08:20.010 --> 08:22.090
We're new in the town
and don't know anyone here.

08:22.090 --> 08:24.010
We'll always end up losing out.

08:24.570 --> 08:25.450
Are you okay?

08:25.450 --> 08:26.810
Well, I'll give you a day off.

08:26.810 --> 08:28.010
Take some rest.

08:28.250 --> 08:29.290
Go ahead.

08:32.490 --> 08:35.289
I thought being nice
would be a good start,

08:35.330 --> 08:36.809
but she has a terrible temper.

08:38.169 --> 08:39.370
Had you gone out earlier,

08:39.370 --> 08:40.850
his hand wouldn't have been scalded.

08:41.490 --> 08:42.890
There's no one I can rely on
in this family.

08:42.929 --> 08:43.409
Order, please.

08:43.610 --> 08:44.370
Coming.

08:45.570 --> 08:47.010
Isn't it inappropriate

08:47.010 --> 08:48.810
for a man to interfere

08:49.650 --> 08:50.490
with women's arguments?

08:56.610 --> 08:57.410
Let me.

09:00.730 --> 09:01.570
Qingyu.

09:02.930 --> 09:03.810
You're always

09:04.170 --> 09:05.050
the sweetheart.

09:05.450 --> 09:06.650
Sir, an extra fried egg, please.

09:07.010 --> 09:07.610
Coming.

09:09.450 --> 09:10.250
I'll do it.

09:11.050 --> 09:12.010
Hey, don't.

09:12.010 --> 09:12.490
Be careful.

09:47.810 --> 09:48.610
Look at this.

09:49.530 --> 09:51.450
I bought it in the morning market.

09:52.250 --> 09:53.370
"May everything go well."

09:53.490 --> 09:54.290
Not bad, right?

09:56.330 --> 09:57.570
That's a good blessing.

09:58.690 --> 09:59.530
But

10:00.690 --> 10:01.610
you've bought

10:01.610 --> 10:03.890
too many useless things here.

10:03.890 --> 10:04.330
Look at these.

10:04.570 --> 10:05.690
They are all useful.

10:06.690 --> 10:08.050
They're worth a fortune, you know?

10:08.530 --> 10:09.490
We need to watch our spending.

10:10.690 --> 10:12.130
There will be plenty of expenses later.

10:13.130 --> 10:13.690
Mom,

10:13.890 --> 10:15.570
I don't want to share a room
with Qingyu.

10:15.890 --> 10:17.050
Sleep on the streets, then.

10:17.130 --> 10:17.490
Exactly.

10:21.690 --> 10:22.850
Mom, where's my gaming console?

10:29.890 --> 10:30.690
All you care about is playing games.

10:33.170 --> 10:34.290
I don't like it here.

10:34.450 --> 10:35.690
Why did we have to move?

10:35.890 --> 10:36.690
What do you think?

10:37.250 --> 10:38.290
It's all because of you two.

10:39.090 --> 10:40.930
This place is better for learning.

11:06.610 --> 11:08.810
[In Memoriam]

13:08.110 --> 13:09.490
[Classmate Record]

13:09.970 --> 13:10.850
Have you straightened everything up?

13:12.970 --> 13:13.770
Mom.

13:15.050 --> 13:17.690
How do you fold this blanket?

13:17.690 --> 13:18.890
What are you even capable of?

13:20.170 --> 13:20.810
Let me see.

13:20.810 --> 13:22.330
Find the corner.

13:22.610 --> 13:23.730
Look at your sister.

13:24.250 --> 13:26.490
So smart and responsible.

13:27.290 --> 13:29.450
Huanzhou High School admitted her

13:29.450 --> 13:30.690
right after seeing
her academic transcript.

13:31.130 --> 13:31.970
You, in contrast,

13:32.250 --> 13:34.010
had a much tougher time
getting into a sports school.

13:34.490 --> 13:35.410
That's right.

13:35.810 --> 13:37.490
Qingyu excels in everything.

13:37.530 --> 13:39.090
Then why did you give birth to me?

13:39.370 --> 13:40.530
You think that was a mistake, huh?

13:40.530 --> 13:41.170
Nonsense.

13:41.170 --> 13:41.970
Mom,

13:41.970 --> 13:43.010
take some rest.

13:43.010 --> 13:44.570
We'll take care of this ourselves.

13:44.970 --> 13:45.730
Did you hear that?

13:45.730 --> 13:46.690
Do this yourself.

13:56.690 --> 13:59.210
You're sensible and intelligent,

13:59.410 --> 14:00.730
but what good is it?

14:01.010 --> 14:03.450
Look how free I am.

14:04.010 --> 14:06.770
Qingyu, I did you a favor just now.

14:07.090 --> 14:09.690
You should treat me to a good meal.

14:10.290 --> 14:11.210
In your dreams.

14:11.930 --> 14:13.810
Is this how you repay your life savior?

14:13.810 --> 14:15.450
Dad and Mom are already stressed enough.

14:15.450 --> 14:16.770
Should I be like you

14:16.770 --> 14:17.770
and irritate them again?

14:18.170 --> 14:19.370
Yes, you're sensible,

14:19.690 --> 14:22.330
but they've never given you any rewards.

14:22.530 --> 14:25.290
On the contrary,
I've been slouching every day,

14:25.930 --> 14:27.850
and they care more about me.

14:28.810 --> 14:31.410
Dad and Mom pay
the least attention to you.

14:31.890 --> 14:32.770
To be frank,

14:33.410 --> 14:36.290
you're kind of a nobody.

14:36.490 --> 14:37.450
Back in Shunyun,

14:37.450 --> 14:40.130
many people thought
I only had one sister,

14:40.370 --> 14:41.170
and it wasn't you.

14:41.610 --> 14:42.890
You want another beating?

14:44.770 --> 14:46.810
I'm telling the truth.

14:48.730 --> 14:49.530
All right.

14:49.730 --> 14:51.210
You're my only sister.

14:51.850 --> 14:53.970
You're my sister forever.

14:54.010 --> 14:54.770
Is that okay?

14:54.770 --> 14:55.930
Talk to the hand.

15:00.290 --> 15:04.310
[Classmate Record]

15:06.910 --> 15:09.640
[May you sail through everything]

15:09.640 --> 15:10.860
[Wish you a bright future.
Everything will be alright.]

15:15.910 --> 15:19.490
[Ma Mingkai]

15:21.210 --> 15:21.970
Qingyu,

15:22.170 --> 15:24.570
it's only the first day of the business,

15:24.970 --> 15:27.210
and my hand almost got burned off.

15:28.290 --> 15:31.170
Is Huanzhou really as great as Mom says?

15:31.170 --> 15:32.970
[So sorry we missed a proper goodbye.
Wishing you all the best!]

15:33.650 --> 15:34.050
Qingyu.

15:34.050 --> 15:34.850
What?

15:35.890 --> 15:38.050
It's not easy to run a business
in a big city.

15:38.290 --> 15:39.050
Mom said this.

15:39.330 --> 15:41.130
Why do you always listen to her?

15:42.050 --> 15:42.810
Honestly,

15:43.290 --> 15:45.010
I know you don't want
to come to Huanzhou.

15:45.490 --> 15:47.850
You were doing great
in Shunyun No. 1 High School

15:48.890 --> 15:50.530
and might have been recommended
for university admission.

15:50.770 --> 15:51.890
Now that you've come to Huanzhou,

15:52.250 --> 15:54.170
your situation has completely changed.

15:54.570 --> 15:56.250
I doubt you're fine with that.

15:56.570 --> 15:58.170
There are more opportunities
in Huanzhou High School.

15:58.450 --> 15:59.250
Perhaps I might

15:59.250 --> 16:00.970
get into a better university
in the future.

16:02.050 --> 16:04.490
Besides, new beginnings

16:04.610 --> 16:05.530
bring

16:05.850 --> 16:07.250
new opportunities.

16:24.090 --> 16:25.050
The nerve of you!

16:25.290 --> 16:26.730
Stand still. Don't run!

16:32.850 --> 16:33.650
Get out of my way!

16:36.090 --> 16:36.690
You're not getting away!

16:36.690 --> 16:37.290
What are you doing?

16:37.810 --> 16:38.410
Run as you want.

16:39.370 --> 16:39.970
Keep running.

16:40.690 --> 16:41.290
Don't move.

16:41.930 --> 16:43.530
Take out the wallet.

16:44.050 --> 16:44.730
I don't have any money.

16:45.130 --> 16:45.730
Where's your money?

16:46.570 --> 16:47.290
Money.

17:13.010 --> 17:14.890
Ma Mingkai, I hope this letter
finds you well.

17:15.609 --> 17:17.849
Everything in Huanzhou is going well.

17:18.450 --> 17:20.410
Right now, I'm sitting
under a banyan tree by a river,

17:20.410 --> 17:21.530
writing to you.

17:22.369 --> 17:24.569
Shunyun and Huanzhou
are only a hundred kilometers apart,

17:25.010 --> 17:26.329
but they're so much different.

17:27.609 --> 17:29.050
You wrote in the classmate record

17:29.370 --> 17:31.410
that you regretted not saying
a proper goodbye to me.

17:31.970 --> 17:35.050
I believe life is full of separations.

17:36.290 --> 17:38.050
But as written in novels,

17:38.450 --> 17:40.170
"No matter how far people are apart,

17:40.490 --> 17:43.650
the sky above us is always the same.

17:45.050 --> 17:46.490
So, we never feel lonely,

17:46.850 --> 17:48.490
no matter where we are."

17:49.290 --> 17:50.970
I hope you'll study hard

17:51.290 --> 17:53.290
and get good grades in NCEE.

17:53.930 --> 17:56.490
Hopefully, we can get into
the same university.

18:11.540 --> 18:13.640
[Ma Mingkai]

18:22.610 --> 18:23.130
Hey.

18:26.170 --> 18:27.010
You ruined my leaf.

18:28.770 --> 18:29.730
Get out of my way!

18:33.010 --> 18:33.970
This isn't yours.

18:35.970 --> 18:37.410
This is my tree.

18:42.770 --> 18:43.450
This banyan tree

18:43.570 --> 18:44.870
[Ficus Altissima Blume]
belongs to Huanzhou Municipal

18:44.870 --> 18:46.450
Forestry and Parks Bureau.

18:46.450 --> 18:48.210
When I said it's mine, it's mine.

18:49.610 --> 18:50.410
This letter.

18:50.970 --> 18:51.690
Qiao Qingyu.

18:52.730 --> 18:54.330
This name sounds familiar.

18:57.330 --> 18:58.450
You can have it if you like.

18:58.650 --> 18:59.530
I don't mind writing it again.

19:01.330 --> 19:02.210
You've got guts.

19:02.970 --> 19:04.010
Do you know who I am?

19:05.730 --> 19:07.210
You don't know me, anyway.

19:08.530 --> 19:09.130
I do.

19:11.490 --> 19:12.730
Beiyu's

19:13.450 --> 19:14.330
little sister.

19:22.770 --> 19:23.330
Are you?

19:35.490 --> 19:37.050
Two, two, three, four.

19:37.490 --> 19:39.610
Five, six, seven.

19:53.770 --> 19:55.890
Qiao Qingyu, let's go.

20:05.850 --> 20:07.730
Wang rented out his rooftop unit.

20:07.730 --> 20:09.090
He rented it out?

20:09.250 --> 20:10.450
Why is ours still vacant?

20:10.450 --> 20:11.850
You're not putting in any effort.

20:11.850 --> 20:12.370
Right.

20:18.690 --> 20:21.050
Hands off.
Mom hasn't eaten any meat yet.

20:22.530 --> 20:23.330
I don't need it.

20:23.570 --> 20:24.890
I eat it every day in the shop.

20:25.890 --> 20:27.570
One of you is always jumping around,

20:27.570 --> 20:29.610
and the other one is studying so hard.

20:33.410 --> 20:34.210
Qingyu,

20:34.490 --> 20:35.770
you need to work harder.

20:35.850 --> 20:37.050
This isn't Shunyun.

20:37.450 --> 20:38.890
Even if you were in the top ten
back there,

20:39.090 --> 20:41.050
you're only an average student here,

20:41.050 --> 20:41.730
right?

20:41.770 --> 20:42.810
But that's fine.

20:43.130 --> 20:44.930
They say everyone in your school
is an ace student.

20:44.930 --> 20:46.650
They all strive hard to study.

20:48.410 --> 20:49.810
I've given up on him.

20:50.370 --> 20:52.290
He just can't study.

20:52.650 --> 20:54.450
If you can get a diploma,

20:54.450 --> 20:55.730
that's the best I could ask for.

20:58.010 --> 20:59.170
So I'm counting on you

20:59.290 --> 21:00.650
to make our family proud, right?

21:02.650 --> 21:03.450
You're home.

21:03.530 --> 21:04.490
I'm home.

21:04.730 --> 21:05.810
Have you eaten yet?

21:06.170 --> 21:06.850
I did.

21:08.770 --> 21:10.370
There weren't any customers before 8 PM.

21:10.850 --> 21:12.530
I waited there for a long time,
but no one came,

21:13.010 --> 21:14.290
so I grabbed some dinner.

21:14.330 --> 21:15.410
Don't be impatient.

21:15.890 --> 21:17.490
It takes time to build a business.

21:17.730 --> 21:18.810
We just opened, after all.

21:19.650 --> 21:20.810
I brought you the medicine.

21:20.850 --> 21:21.650
Take them on time.

21:21.650 --> 21:22.130
All right.

21:22.130 --> 21:23.650
Don't let your injuries act up again.

21:24.210 --> 21:25.290
I know.

21:32.560 --> 21:35.260
[Painkiller]

22:08.590 --> 22:11.010
[Adolescent Sexual Health
Education Textbook]

22:20.930 --> 22:21.770
Qingyu.

22:23.370 --> 22:25.290
You're a grown-up girl.

22:26.890 --> 22:29.010
As a girl in school,

22:29.330 --> 22:31.810
you need to be careful
with what you do and say.

22:33.570 --> 22:35.170
Stay away from
those who don't study well

22:35.170 --> 22:36.210
and are a bad influence.

22:37.010 --> 22:38.330
Safety comes first.

22:43.570 --> 22:45.330
If it were just me and your dad,

22:45.330 --> 22:46.570
we could live anywhere.

22:46.650 --> 22:47.770
We went through all the hassle

22:47.770 --> 22:49.170
just for the sake of you two.

22:49.530 --> 22:51.410
We want to give you a better environment

22:52.090 --> 22:53.650
in which you can focus on your studies.

22:53.890 --> 22:54.410
Ouch!

22:55.810 --> 22:56.930
What's wrong with you?

22:56.930 --> 22:58.450
Why are you having trouble with this?

23:05.250 --> 23:06.170
Let me see.

23:06.570 --> 23:07.530
Is it a deep cut?

23:37.490 --> 23:39.330
Why keep this unlucky stuff?

23:41.210 --> 23:43.490
Those were her last pair of shoes.

23:44.410 --> 23:45.770
Her belongings.

23:46.210 --> 23:47.890
She looked so beautiful dancing on stage

23:47.890 --> 23:50.450
in those shoes.

23:50.490 --> 23:51.610
Everyone in Shunyun

23:51.610 --> 23:53.930
knows Qiao Beiyu.

23:55.450 --> 23:56.410
Mom said

23:56.410 --> 23:57.930
once we moved to Huanzhou,

23:57.930 --> 23:59.250
there was no such person
in this family anymore.

24:00.770 --> 24:02.210
Mom again.

24:02.970 --> 24:04.090
Well,

24:04.410 --> 24:06.370
she's our sister after all.

24:06.370 --> 24:07.250
She is not.

24:08.330 --> 24:08.930
Sch.

24:09.130 --> 24:09.890
What's with that scoff?

24:11.450 --> 24:12.730
Whatever you truly think about,

24:12.930 --> 24:14.890
you just repeat everything Mom says.

24:15.410 --> 24:16.210
Qiao Jinyu!

24:16.370 --> 24:16.850
Aw!

24:19.010 --> 24:19.730
Well.

24:20.850 --> 24:21.490
I mean,

24:23.530 --> 24:25.250
you're the first child,
and I'm the second child.

24:25.970 --> 24:27.730
Anyway, not many people here know us.

24:38.530 --> 24:39.970
You don't know me, anyway.

24:40.250 --> 24:41.170
I do.

24:42.370 --> 24:44.250
Beiyu's

24:44.250 --> 24:45.090
little sister.

25:09.290 --> 25:11.570
Isn't this Beiyu's little sister?

25:12.050 --> 25:13.490
Stay.

25:14.250 --> 25:15.090
Oh, nice.

25:15.330 --> 25:15.770
You're pretty.

25:15.770 --> 25:16.330
I don't know you.

25:16.330 --> 25:17.370
We know you.

25:17.610 --> 25:19.170
Where are you going?

25:20.130 --> 25:21.370
Don't go.

25:21.690 --> 25:22.610
Go away.

25:39.040 --> 25:46.140
[Huanzhou High School]

26:05.090 --> 26:07.160
[School Compound Floor Map]

26:08.330 --> 26:09.970
Meixi, wait for me.

26:10.370 --> 26:11.770
Where did you go during the break?

26:12.210 --> 26:14.370
My dad took me to Hong Kong, China
for a concert.

26:14.810 --> 26:15.770
That's wonderful.

26:15.810 --> 26:17.530
I wish I could go to a concert.

26:28.490 --> 26:30.890
A warning demerit isn't that bad.

26:31.290 --> 26:32.610
Once or twice isn't a problem.

26:33.010 --> 26:34.130
His father's the problem.

26:34.330 --> 26:35.770
He's difficult to deal with.

26:36.890 --> 26:39.570
Why do you think

26:39.570 --> 26:40.650
Sun wanted us

26:40.650 --> 26:42.530
to post Sheng's demerit notice?

26:42.530 --> 26:44.250
He knows we're tight.

26:44.250 --> 26:44.960
[Huanzhou High School]
This is

26:44.960 --> 26:46.130
[Demerit Notice for Ming Sheng]
a warning for us.

26:47.530 --> 26:48.490
Ming Sheng?

26:50.410 --> 26:51.690
Why aren't you in your uniform?

26:52.170 --> 26:52.970
Are you a newcomer?

26:54.250 --> 26:55.250
Sun mentioned

26:55.250 --> 26:56.730
there would be a new transfer student.

26:57.450 --> 26:58.490
Are you the one?

26:59.610 --> 27:01.730
I'm Qiao Qingyu, the new transfer
to Class 5, Grade 2.

27:01.930 --> 27:02.930
Oh, it's really you.

27:03.330 --> 27:03.850
What a fate.

27:04.370 --> 27:05.970
Let me introduce myself. I'm Ye Zilin.

27:06.650 --> 27:08.050
Chen Hao.

27:08.410 --> 27:08.890
Hello.

27:11.410 --> 27:13.770
Our class is assigned to clean
the natatorium this morning.

27:14.250 --> 27:15.010
How about this?

27:15.450 --> 27:16.610
We'll take you there now.

27:16.730 --> 27:18.050
You don't have to go to the classroom.

27:18.050 --> 27:19.930
Yeah. No one's in the classroom now.

27:20.650 --> 27:21.490
The natatorium is over there.

27:21.490 --> 27:21.970
Let's go.

27:21.970 --> 27:22.610
Come.

27:23.370 --> 27:24.090
Come. Let's go.

27:24.090 --> 27:24.850
This way.

27:36.570 --> 27:37.130
Over here.

27:39.890 --> 27:41.930
Cleaning the natatorium
in the early morning, eh?

27:42.370 --> 27:43.650
Who arranged this?

27:44.570 --> 27:45.610
Stop complaining.

27:45.810 --> 27:47.010
Consider it as exercise.

27:48.650 --> 27:49.810
Qiao,

27:50.330 --> 27:51.850
see those coiled lane lines?

27:52.210 --> 27:53.170
Go and fix them.

27:57.690 --> 27:58.930
Isn't that your job?

27:59.090 --> 28:01.250
Let the newcomer have a chance.

28:12.530 --> 28:13.610
Here. Take this.

28:18.130 --> 28:19.170
It's almost time for morning study.

28:19.170 --> 28:20.450
Why hasn't anyone shown up yet?

28:20.530 --> 28:22.610
Don't tell me only a few of us
cleaning up all this.

28:22.610 --> 28:23.450
Tell me about it.

28:24.090 --> 28:26.010
They have no team spirit whatsoever.

28:29.130 --> 28:29.730
Hey.

28:29.730 --> 28:30.730
She fell in.

28:30.970 --> 28:32.050
Help her!

28:35.010 --> 28:36.010
Who fell into the pool?

28:36.010 --> 28:37.650
What are you standing here for?
Save her!

28:37.970 --> 28:38.890
Grab this.

28:44.810 --> 28:46.530
Ye Zilin, was it you?

28:46.690 --> 28:47.410
Not me.

28:47.410 --> 28:48.690
I didn't know how she fell in.

28:48.690 --> 28:49.490
Was it you?

28:50.050 --> 28:51.050
I didn't see anything.

28:53.570 --> 28:55.130
Who is this?

28:59.260 --> 29:01.460
[Class 5, Grade 2, Senior High]

29:20.650 --> 29:21.930
Enough. Quiet.

29:23.810 --> 29:26.010
Let me see who's so talkative.

29:27.450 --> 29:30.210
Qiao Qingyu just transferred here

29:30.210 --> 29:31.890
from Shunyun No. 1 High School.

29:31.890 --> 29:33.850
Despite an initial setback,

29:34.010 --> 29:36.010
I believe in the days to come,

29:36.410 --> 29:38.010
Qingyu will definitely feel

29:38.010 --> 29:39.530
the fiery passion

29:39.890 --> 29:41.090
of our class.

29:44.010 --> 29:45.010
What's wrong with you guys?

29:45.450 --> 29:47.650
Do you want to take home
a few more papers

29:47.810 --> 29:50.010
to fuel your passion?

29:53.210 --> 29:54.010
All right.

29:56.010 --> 29:56.810
Qiao Qingyu,

29:57.050 --> 29:58.930
you'll sit next to Jiang Nian.

29:59.250 --> 30:00.890
If you have any questions,
go to Liu Jia.

30:00.890 --> 30:01.970
She's our class monitor.

30:05.090 --> 30:06.330
Alright Class, please turn to

30:06.330 --> 30:07.770
the third section of Chapter two.

30:09.930 --> 30:11.890
Thank you for lending me your uniform.

30:11.890 --> 30:12.690
You're welcome.

30:16.410 --> 30:18.130
My mom's also from Shunyun.

30:18.210 --> 30:19.850
So we're practically
from the same hometown.

30:38.770 --> 30:40.050
How come she fell into the pool?

30:40.090 --> 30:41.810
Who fell into the pool?

30:52.690 --> 30:54.330
What are you standing here for?
Save her!

30:55.050 --> 30:56.210
Grab this.

31:05.370 --> 31:06.930
Who is this?

31:27.290 --> 31:28.610
Hurry up.

31:30.570 --> 31:31.570
Here are some tips for you.

31:31.610 --> 31:33.170
Keep your distance from them.

31:33.290 --> 31:34.130
They're notorious

31:34.130 --> 31:36.130
for being the worst students
in our grade.

31:36.610 --> 31:38.210
Ye Zilin, a transient student.

31:38.370 --> 31:39.930
No matter how poor his NCEE grade is,

31:40.090 --> 31:42.090
he'll inherit his family's shoe factory.

31:42.930 --> 31:44.490
Chen Hao is a sports student.

31:44.490 --> 31:45.770
A long jumper.

31:45.850 --> 31:48.050
He's already pre-admitted
to Huanzhou Sport University.

31:48.130 --> 31:50.250
They may be terrible in their studies,

31:50.250 --> 31:52.290
but they're best
when it comes to pranks.

31:53.290 --> 31:54.370
As for Ming Sheng...

31:54.370 --> 31:55.130
Beiyu's little sister.

32:06.770 --> 32:07.770
You got the wrong person.

32:14.910 --> 32:19.690
[The proper way to protect yourself
from harassment]

32:19.690 --> 32:22.170
When sexual harassment or assault

32:22.170 --> 32:23.210
happens,

32:23.770 --> 32:26.090
dealing with it wisely and bravely

32:26.090 --> 32:28.090
can help stop it.

32:28.650 --> 32:31.130
Don't be weak or helpless.

32:31.530 --> 32:33.610
If attacked, shout for help

32:33.610 --> 32:35.770
to distract the perpetrator

32:36.450 --> 32:37.930
and signal for assistance.

32:37.930 --> 32:40.090
These are the correct ways
to deal with the situation.

32:42.050 --> 32:44.130
As for high school students,

32:44.130 --> 32:45.530
especially girls,

32:46.010 --> 32:49.330
where does harassment
most commonly happen?

32:50.810 --> 32:51.970
The newcomer,

32:52.570 --> 32:54.290
please stand up and answer.

33:01.730 --> 33:04.010
Page 34, third section.

33:23.190 --> 33:24.360
[Qiao Qingyu]

33:24.570 --> 33:26.010
Qiao Qingyu,

33:26.610 --> 33:29.690
where does harassment commonly happen?

33:35.850 --> 33:37.650
Ma'am, I know why

33:37.650 --> 33:38.850
she can't answer your question.

33:39.970 --> 33:41.170
Qiao Qingyu,

33:41.170 --> 33:43.090
why is it all blacked out?

33:44.090 --> 33:46.090
Are you highlighting the main points?

33:46.090 --> 33:47.250
I can't read them clearly.

33:47.250 --> 33:48.770
Ye, what's wrong with you?

33:48.770 --> 33:50.010
You shouldn't touch girls' things
without asking.

33:50.010 --> 33:51.210
You're disrespecting girls.

33:51.210 --> 33:51.690
Ma'am.

33:53.130 --> 33:54.170
I'm so sorry.

33:54.770 --> 33:55.930
That being said, Qiao Qingyu,

33:55.930 --> 33:57.210
you're living so righteously.

33:57.850 --> 33:58.810
Are you from the ancient times?

33:59.490 --> 34:00.770
Please behave.

34:03.650 --> 34:04.770
For a long time,

34:04.770 --> 34:06.970
the lack of knowledge
about physiological hygiene

34:06.970 --> 34:09.610
has made any discussion
about intimacy a sensitive topic.

34:10.370 --> 34:11.929
I hope that through this session,

34:11.929 --> 34:13.210
physiological hygiene

34:13.210 --> 34:15.969
will become as common a topic
as eating and sleeping.

34:28.290 --> 34:29.650
Why are you still up?

34:30.010 --> 34:31.250
My slippers.

34:35.610 --> 34:36.810
Are you not feeling well?

34:37.610 --> 34:38.850
Hurry and go to sleep.

34:38.929 --> 34:40.409
You have to go to school early tomorrow.

34:42.610 --> 34:43.690
Did you do something to my textbook?

34:47.050 --> 34:47.530
Hmm.

34:49.210 --> 34:50.010
What's wrong?

34:50.929 --> 34:52.050
Did you argue with someone at school?

34:53.370 --> 34:54.409
Is the food at the canteen terrible?

34:54.850 --> 34:56.889
You can cancel the school meal
starting tomorrow.

34:57.250 --> 34:59.050
We'll prepare your lunch,

34:59.050 --> 34:59.810
and you can take it to school.

34:59.930 --> 35:01.570
It's not about food.

35:01.610 --> 35:03.450
You're not adjusting to the new school?

35:03.650 --> 35:05.650
Don't worry.
Try to make some new friends.

35:05.730 --> 35:06.130
Right?

35:06.130 --> 35:08.170
You'll get used to it over time.

35:11.250 --> 35:12.050
What's this?

35:16.690 --> 35:17.930
These are useless.

35:18.050 --> 35:18.850
It's not tested in NCEE.

35:18.850 --> 35:19.930
Do not read this nonsense.

35:19.930 --> 35:21.450
This is a school textbook.

35:22.450 --> 35:23.450
I don't care about others,

35:23.650 --> 35:24.410
but you can't read

35:24.410 --> 35:25.570
this nonsense.

35:25.770 --> 35:27.370
It's part of the curriculum.

35:28.370 --> 35:31.130
Qiao Qingyu, how old are you?

35:31.250 --> 35:32.050
You're 17.

35:32.050 --> 35:33.770
You're a 17-year-old girl.

35:33.930 --> 35:36.210
Why do you need to read such nonsense?

35:39.050 --> 35:40.370
You didn't teach Qiao Beiyu back then,

35:40.370 --> 35:41.650
that's why she ended up like that.

35:41.970 --> 35:43.690
She ended up that way

35:43.850 --> 35:44.970
because she read nonsense

35:44.970 --> 35:45.970
like this!

35:47.010 --> 35:48.810
Well, be nice.

35:48.810 --> 35:49.730
You...

35:49.730 --> 35:51.010
Didn't we agree

35:51.330 --> 35:53.330
not to bring this up again
after moving to Huanzhou?

35:59.010 --> 36:00.170
It's late now.

36:00.290 --> 36:01.850
You're disturbing my sleep.

36:03.250 --> 36:04.970
Right. They have to go
to school tomorrow.

36:05.010 --> 36:05.650
Go to sleep.

36:05.650 --> 36:07.130
School's tomorrow,
so get an early night.

36:10.810 --> 36:12.170
All right. Go to sleep.

36:18.450 --> 36:20.050
Don't be mad. The girl didn't mean it.

36:21.930 --> 36:22.850
I did.

36:43.370 --> 36:44.210
Qiao Qingyu.

36:46.130 --> 36:46.970
Qiao Qingyu!

36:49.010 --> 36:50.210
Why are you walking away so fast?

36:50.610 --> 36:51.450
We're classmates.

36:51.450 --> 36:52.850
We'll have plenty of chances to meet.

36:52.850 --> 36:54.010
What exactly do you want?

36:54.890 --> 36:56.210
How are you going to compensate me?

36:57.170 --> 36:58.170
Bite me back

36:58.170 --> 36:59.250
and we're even.

37:03.890 --> 37:05.050
If it were someone else,

37:05.050 --> 37:06.410
the consequences would be different.

37:07.370 --> 37:08.970
But you're an intelligent student,

37:09.090 --> 37:10.610
so I'll go easy on you.

37:15.010 --> 37:15.770
My hand hurts.

37:15.770 --> 37:16.690
I can't do my homework.

37:16.810 --> 37:17.530
You do it for me.

37:18.170 --> 37:19.290
I've just transferred here

37:19.290 --> 37:20.410
and have a lot to catch up on.

37:20.410 --> 37:21.570
I don't have time to help you with that.

37:27.610 --> 37:28.490
You don't have time?

37:29.570 --> 37:30.770
Don't you want to know

37:30.770 --> 37:32.130
What really happened

37:32.130 --> 37:32.930
to your sister?

37:48.810 --> 37:53.970
- Go!
- Come on!

38:01.330 --> 38:03.650
- Go!
- Go!

38:21.690 --> 38:22.490
You don't have time?

38:23.490 --> 38:24.890
Don't you want to know

38:24.890 --> 38:26.890
what really happened to your sister?

38:49.460 --> 38:52.210
[Shunyun]

38:52.210 --> 38:53.490
Isn't that Qiao?

38:55.930 --> 38:57.490
It's said she died of AIDS.

38:57.890 --> 38:58.690
AIDS?

38:58.690 --> 38:59.330
Yeah.

39:01.010 --> 39:02.770
She died at a very young age.

39:04.210 --> 39:05.090
Oh.

39:05.090 --> 39:06.210
What a pity.

39:13.290 --> 39:14.290
Let's eat here.

39:16.740 --> 39:19.390
[Qiao's Handmade Noodle House]

39:27.570 --> 39:28.370
Be careful.

39:34.170 --> 39:34.730
Higher.

39:34.730 --> 39:35.610
[Shop for Transfer]

39:35.610 --> 39:36.170
Higher.

39:36.930 --> 39:39.690
Once we leave here,
we can say goodbye to the past

39:40.370 --> 39:42.090
and start over.

40:10.130 --> 40:11.130
Are you done with your homework?

40:11.730 --> 40:12.290
Hmm.

40:13.650 --> 40:14.850
Are you adjusting well to school?

40:15.570 --> 40:16.410
Quite well.

40:18.570 --> 40:19.810
Are you keeping up with the syllabus?

40:20.010 --> 40:20.610
Hmm.

40:21.410 --> 40:22.290
They say

40:22.610 --> 40:23.930
students at your school

40:24.010 --> 40:26.730
don't just do questions from textbooks.

40:27.250 --> 40:28.810
They also do extra

40:28.970 --> 40:31.010
or even more advanced questions.

40:32.170 --> 40:34.370
You need to push yourself hard.

40:34.610 --> 40:36.330
If not, the gap between you and them
will grow bigger,

40:36.330 --> 40:37.690
and you won't catch up with them.

40:39.050 --> 40:39.850
Oh, right.

40:42.250 --> 40:43.530
Aunt Qin is sick again.

40:43.770 --> 40:45.530
Go to the bank this Sunday

40:46.010 --> 40:47.610
to send 500 yuan to Uncle Jiangsheng

40:47.610 --> 40:48.610
in Nanqiao Village.

40:52.130 --> 40:54.890
What's Aunt Qin sick with?

40:56.490 --> 40:58.010
They say she had a mental problem.

40:58.490 --> 41:00.650
Her condition has been unstable
over these years.

41:00.650 --> 41:01.930
Your uncle has been taking her
for treatments,

41:02.290 --> 41:04.290
but there's no improvement.

41:04.570 --> 41:06.810
What's wrong with me?
I keep calling her Aunt Qin like you.

41:06.850 --> 41:07.930
I can't change it.

41:08.690 --> 41:10.690
What about Qiao Beiyu, then?

41:10.730 --> 41:12.250
Dad and you never mentioned it.

41:12.450 --> 41:13.250
Wait.

41:13.450 --> 41:14.570
It was appendicitis.

41:15.650 --> 41:16.930
I told you before.

41:18.690 --> 41:20.170
There were complications after surgery.

41:21.730 --> 41:23.290
But everyone says she had AIDS.

41:25.210 --> 41:26.690
What... What AIDS?

41:26.690 --> 41:27.490
Who told you that?

41:27.490 --> 41:28.850
Nonsense! These are simply rumors!

41:28.970 --> 41:30.010
If it's nonsense,

41:30.010 --> 41:31.210
why didn't you argue with them?

41:32.330 --> 41:33.490
How?

41:34.250 --> 41:35.210
How am I even able

41:35.210 --> 41:36.730
to argue with so many people?

41:36.730 --> 41:37.730
You are so ignorant.

41:37.730 --> 41:38.970
Words can kill, you know?

41:39.330 --> 41:40.090
But if we don't make it clear,

41:40.090 --> 41:41.570
we keep getting bullied
and dragged into trouble,

41:41.610 --> 41:42.810
no matter where we go.

41:42.810 --> 41:44.210
Who bullied you?

41:44.210 --> 41:45.370
We've already moved to a new place.

41:45.370 --> 41:46.210
She's dead.

41:46.210 --> 41:47.330
Everything is in the past.

41:47.330 --> 41:48.250
No, it's not.

41:49.330 --> 41:50.290
What do you want, then?

42:22.260 --> 42:25.950
♪Perhaps♪

42:26.460 --> 42:32.160
♪The more we care,
the more careful we become♪

42:33.300 --> 42:38.700
♪Counting the distance
that separates us♪

42:39.700 --> 42:45.260
♪A single step,
and we'd be closer still♪

42:50.930 --> 42:54.600
♪In the future♪

42:55.060 --> 43:00.780
♪Time will reveal this secret♪

43:02.280 --> 43:07.350
♪Waiting is a silent promise♪

43:08.600 --> 43:13.760
♪That never expires♪

43:17.360 --> 43:21.830
♪Turns out that what's on my mind♪

43:22.830 --> 43:26.500
♪Is your name♪

43:27.000 --> 43:32.100
♪The only stubbornness in my heart♪

43:33.180 --> 43:36.400
♪At first sight♪

43:36.830 --> 43:40.110
♪The future has been determined♪

43:40.800 --> 43:46.360
♪Dreams began to feel real♪

43:47.460 --> 43:51.000
♪Turns out that what's on your mind♪

43:51.460 --> 43:55.400
♪Is a place♪

43:55.700 --> 44:01.260
♪Where the same story is held dear♪

44:01.930 --> 44:05.300
♪Fortunately, I'm not sensible enough♪

44:05.630 --> 44:09.100
♪Courage wasn't late too♪

44:09.630 --> 44:15.700
♪Only then does time not betray
our acquaintance♪
